OL,3,CMan arrested over allegations of race
OL,4,Cfixing
OL,6,FA 42-year-old man has been arrested
OL,7,Fover allegations of race fixing.
OL,9,FThe arrest took place in Hawkshaw,
OL,10,FBury, on 12 September after a joint
OL,11,Finvestigation by Greater Manchester
OL,12,FPolice and the Gambling Commission.
OL,14,FThe man was alleged to have committed
OL,15,Foffences under section 42 of the
OL,16,FGambling Act which states that it is
OL,17,Fan offence to "cheat at gambling" or
OL,18,Fif someone "does anything for the
OL,19,Fpurpose of enabling or assisting
OL,20,Fanother person to cheat at gambling".
