OL,8,Fearlier this year.
OL,10,FA statement from the Gambling
OL,11,FCommision on Friday read: "The 42-year-
OL,12,Fold was arrested as part of a joint
OL,13,Finvestigation by Greater Manchester
OL,14,FPolice and the Gambling Commission.
OL,16,F"The man, who was arrested in
OL,17,FHawkshaw, Bury, at 6am, is alleged to
OL,18,Fhave committed offences under section
OL,19,F42 of the Gambling Act 2005.
